Clash of clans is a tower game rush game. It has two people there is twenty four arena's in total. There is also a game mode having 2v2 instead of 1v1 there is also activities of different modes like three times elexa or gold rush mode.
U can have many different type of strategies due to the large variety of cards
Brawl stars is a multi mode pvp game that there is many different modes like gem grab, bounty, showdown, heist, brawl ball, siege, hot zone, and duo showdown. There is also a large variety of brawlers that u can use. There is also a large variety of maps that u can play on. There is also a large variety of strategies that u can use. 